							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The old training options are all gone now with the revamp and replaced with master 2 versions of core skills instead.  So every 10 levels you can choose one skill from a list of 4 to upgrade to master 2.  Some special skills like the dirge run speed choice are getting added to the core sub class skills.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Rogue
<br />
Level 14:
<br />
Backstab 
<br />
Quick Flurry 
<br />
Street Smarts 
<br />
Circular Strike
<br />

<br />
Predator
<br />

<br />
Level 14:
<br />
