						<tr>
							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hey, this ties into this thread somehwhat so I thought I'd post here.
<br />

<br />
I logged onto my lvl 17 bard on the test server to check out LU #13e-- <a href="http://eqiiforums.station.sony.com/eq2/board/message?board.id=tup&amp;message.id=65#M65" target="_blank" class="postlink">here are the patch notes</a>
<br />

<br />
The old training choices are gone, but the new Master2s don't show up for you unless you've been saving up a /respec, so I didn't get to test any of those.
<br />

<br />
There were a few other interesting things people might like to know though. Ensnare is now a coin spell for HOs, so scouts now have 4 coin spells instead of 3. We also have one less cloak spell then, so there's a trade-off. Some of the other HO icons may have changed too, but this one caught my eye.
<br />

<br />
Rare harvests have been made much more common! How much? Well, people were chatting about it on the test channel so I had to try it out. In about 4 hours I harvested 3 rares (one severed bone, one blackened iron and one silver cluster) and about 5 glowing uncommon ones. I wasn't even working entirely on harvesting as I was trying to get MOBs to attack me while harvesting to raise my "focus" skill. So, currently rare harvests are appearing at about one per hour. This may be changed still before it hits the live servers so don't go crazy. For now, I can only say don't spend a ton of money on buying any rares! Having all Adept 3s and rare crafted gear may become the norm for serious players.
<br />

<br />
I like the new ranges of con colors. At lvl 17, 17 was white, 15+16 were blue, and 12-14 were green. This gives you a wider range of things to fight in each area.
<br />

<br />
One last thing I noticed, while grouped, was that I could have Bria's on (the bard's power regen song) and stay invisible while the tank pulled and Bria's didn't break my invis. This has been messed up for months and months so I hope this is officially changed and fixed.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
						</tr>
					</table></td>
				</tr>
